    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >「在纸张的边缘，一个小火柴人被画了出来。」</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Pengame》是一款纯手工打造的 2D 射击平台游戏，拥有完整语音演出的故事战役，舞台设定在一本笔记本中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/494240/extras/d38bd449f89cd2f6e407cec6e7e15d98.poster.avif?t=1771269936\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/494240/extras/d38bd449f89cd2f6e407cec6e7e15d98.webm?t=1771269936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/494240/extras/d38bd449f89cd2f6e407cec6e7e15d98.mp4?t=1771269936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >「敌人的数量在增加。很好，他想—那是一个明确的迹象，表明他正逐渐接近命定之地。」</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位课堂中感到无聊的学生，在笔记本中创造了一个广阔的世界。<br>原本这里一片和平，直到他犯下一个可怕的错误：他在神圣的纸上画出了他所能想象的最恐怖的怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身为火柴人战斗吧！<br>你是无数被选中的人之一，注定要净化这个被老师的邪恶力量腐蚀的手绘世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/494240/extras/aa84b0a871a0c371dcf6209300340e6d.poster.avif?t=1771269936\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/494240/extras/aa84b0a871a0c371dcf6209300340e6d.webm?t=1771269936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/494240/extras/aa84b0a871a0c371dcf6209300340e6d.mp4?t=1771269936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >「射击确实挺有意思的，到目前为止，这大概是我对自己唯一的了解。」</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗与探索是《Pengame》的核心。火柴人天生擅长跳跃，还拥有违反常理的时间操控能力。他能使用多种武器，每种都有其优点与限制。若想在敌众我寡的情况下生存下来，并穿越笔记本中最危险的区域，<br>你必须精通他的武器库与时间操控技巧。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双重跳跃与墙跳</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞬移冲刺</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四种独特枪械，每种都有副射击模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种可暂时使用的超级武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可使用传说中的圣剑「王者之剑」，进行近战攻击</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间操控能力（子弹时间与时间倒流）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/494240/extras/d8d47cc52ea06fcd8f2b3f9880493ddd.poster.avif?t=1771269936\" aria-hidden=\"true\"width=800 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/494240/extras/d8d47cc52ea06fcd8f2b3f9880493ddd.webm?t=1771269936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/494240/extras/d8d47cc52ea06fcd8f2b3f9880493ddd.mp4?t=1771269936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >「那位老牛仔对这名新勇者心存怀疑。他见过太多失败者，但看着自己的世界逐渐腐朽，他已没有挑剔的余地。」</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会在《Pengame》中发现什么？</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘纸上风格与逐帧动画（全部手工绘制）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原创且全语音演出的故事战役</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 40 种独特敌人类型和 7 个 Boss 战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >线性剧情推进，穿越精心打造的关卡，并可自由探索。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「试炼模式」让你在通关后继续挑战极限</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
